'''Time bombs''' were generally miniature [[Seismic charge/Legends|seismic charges]] that detonated after about five (or ten) seconds after activation. They were used by [[Pilot/Legends|pilots]] to destroy the major systems of [[Capital ship/Legends|capital ships]] from the inside, as well as by [[Infantry/Legends|infantry]] for other sabotage purposes. [[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] [[Bothan Spynet/Legends|spies]] also used time bombs. Time bombs were also used by [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee]] [[Smuggler/Legends|smugglers]] to destroy gun posts and light Vehicles. The first manufacturers are unknown, though rumor had it that the inhabitants of [[Mon Calamari/Legends|Mon Calamari]] were the first designers.

Some time bombs were also improvised. A notable example are TIE/LN starfighters, where misaligning an energizer for its eponymous engines even slightly will have them turn into improvised time bombs.

